@Nerphice, in fact you will end up with 0 cards in your library if this doesn't hit a non-permanent.  
Yes, you may put it onto the battlefield, but if you don't it just stays exiled.  

So long as you have something that gives your guys haste, you should destroy them that turn ([Concordant Crossroads](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Concordant Crossroads) in Green works).
